item.description:
In an election where no one knows what's going to happen after the votes are counted, hear what leaders of four of the Parliamentary parties have to say... in English.  <br/><br/> Hear clips from the first four party leader interviews Radio Sweden has done so far:
-Jonas Sjöstedt, leader of the Left party;
-Stefan Löfven, leader of the Social Democrats and Prime Minister;
-Jan Björklund, leader of the Liberals;
-Jimmie Åkesson, leader of the Sweden Democrats.
We also go through the spate of car arsons this week, and you'll learn how to find out if your kids get bullied when they go back to school when we speak to Magnus Loftsson, research coordinator for the anti-bullying organization Friends. We also talk about online bullying.
Reporters: Nathalie Rothschild, Ulla Engberg, Loukas Christodoulou, Henrik Torehammar
Producer: Brett Ascarelli

